WEBVTT

00:03.700 --> 00:06.000
My name is Melinda Gordon.

00:06.100 --> 00:07.300
I'm married,

00:07.400 --> 00:09.400
I live in a small town,

00:09.500 --> 00:11.500
and I own an antique shop.

00:11.600 --> 00:13.600
I might be just like you.

00:13.700 --> 00:15.400
Except that from the time
I was a little girl,

00:15.500 --> 00:17.900
I knew that I could talk to the dead.

00:18.000 --> 00:19.100
It's all right, honey.

00:19.200 --> 00:22.300
Earthbound spirits,
my grandmother called them.

00:22.408 --> 00:25.000
They're stuck here, because they have
unfinished business with the living,

00:25.104 --> 00:28.801
and they come to me for help.

00:30.303 --> 00:35.708
In order to tell you my story,
I have to tell you theirs.

00:37.000 --> 00:43.074
